Interface AppWindow

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface AppWindow
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'App Window'. Finestra applicativa comprendente le parti comuni a tutte le schermate e la parte variabile.

    The following features are supported:

    • Footer
    • Header
    • App Area
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getAppWindow()
